    "body": "There is a longer term plan to minimize the diff and use the correct abstractions such that we can attempt to automate the process of merging upstream. Ideally, Optimismtic Geth is defined by a patch file on top of geth. This problem is currently mitigated by permissioned contract deployment.\r\n\r\nWithin a few months, we will shift engineering efforts towards migrating the current optimistic geth codebase to upstream geth.",
